Class CreditHistory

java.lang.Object
CreditHistory
public class CreditHistory extends Object
The CreditHistory class represents the credit history of an individual or entity. It includes information such as bankruptcies, collections, foreclosures, delinquencies, outstanding judgments, dates of last bankruptcy, foreclosure dates, and party to lawsuit status.
